item.description: This month we are going to focus on how to build your list and following. Whether you are a coach, consultant, subject matter expert, massage therapist...no matter what your profession growing a solid list of potential clients is crucial to your ongoing business success. Even if you see yourself as only able to provide services in a particular geographic area you will be sure to learn something that can help you attract new clients.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be in the large ballroom. Go to entrance to the far left of the building.
